{"tid":1222332,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「引渡惡法」外交部罕見傳召美駐華官員 就「不負責言行」嚴正交涉","createTime":"2019-06-14T11:48:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T14:23:09.000Z","uid":201266,"like":4,"dislike":252,"uniUserReply":77,"replies":[{"pid":"68da1a1e48196edbfb513d915332ddf57156f9d3","tid":1222332,"uid":201266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T11:48:37.000Z","msg":"中國外交部副部長樂玉成，今日緊急召見美國駐華使館臨時代辦傅德恩（Robert Forden），就美國對香港政府推動修訂《逃犯條例》和《刑事事宜相互法律協助條例》的不負責任言行提出嚴正交涉。<br />\n<br />\n樂玉成指出，「香港是中國的香港」，「香港事務純屬中國內政，不容任何外部勢力插手置喙」。他續稱：「近來美方一些高級官員頻頻就特區政府推進修例說三道四，橫加干預，中方對此強烈不滿和堅決反對」。<br />\n<br />\n樂玉成敦促美方要「客觀公正看待香港特區政府依法修例」，「切實尊重特區政府正常的立法進程」，「立即停止以任何形式，干預香港事務，不做任何損害香港繁榮穩定的事。中方將視美方行動作出進一步反應」。"},{"pid":"9e897e93d14e6c254798bd4edfa4900935960db8","tid":1222332,"uid":201266,"like":113,"dislike":0,"score":113,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T11:48:59.000Z","msg":"厲害了我的國！"},{"pid":"d7ca32bf60eea4d88e257f228d54675b18fe3dab","tid":1222332,"uid":59868,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T11:49:01.000Z","msg":"中你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6da669943fff9ba0b3ff656ff2b61588376e5f9a","tid":1222332,"uid":201266,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T11:49:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190614&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=59716504\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190614%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D59716504&d=Q%2BwKghBkVpQFldJLXg3PjR5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=26d56c3b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190614%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D59716504&h=d0c5bca1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190614&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=59716504</a>"},{"pid":"44e9cc55d7e3584